OL,5, A Glasgow priest has been convicted of 
OL,6, sexually abusing four girls.           
OL,8,FFather Neil McGarrity, who has been    
OL,9,Fadded to the sex offenders register,   
OL,10,Ftargeted his victims at two churches as
OL,11,Fwell as his parish home.               
OL,13,FThe 68-year-old was found guilty at    
OL,14,FGlasgow Sheriff Court of four sexual   
OL,15,Fassaults and one charge of engaging in 
OL,16,Fsexual activity.                       
OL,18,FThe charges span from December 2017 to 
OL,19,FFebruary 2020, with the girls aged     
OL,20,Fbetween 10 and 16.                     
